These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, country
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of country##1
2. the fan of country is not to the right of the fan of country##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | country | soul |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, family
1. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: pony, mouse
1. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
3. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | pony | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, trike
1. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | airplane | trike |

 #################################

 
